{"tid":2140713,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"美國駐華使領館：大使館拍賣財物非準備撤離","createTime":"2020-08-05T07:34:40.000Z","updateTime":"2020-08-05T08:38:11.000Z","uid":21470,"like":1,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":11,"replies":[{"pid":"0354c951f99e9c5a05bda43837cc18c71a7a5e92","tid":2140713,"uid":21470,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-08-05T07:34:40.000Z","msg":"美國駐華使領館：大使館拍賣財物非準備撤離 <br />\n兩岸 發佈時間 2020-08-05 14:47<br />\n<br />\n美國駐華使領館在社交網站指，位於北京的美國駐華大使館拍賣財物，不代表準備撤離。使領館指，大使館會定期更換舊家具、車輛和其他物品，通常每年安排1至4次拍賣，處置美國政府不再需要的財產，強調是大使館更替二手物品的正常安排。<br />\n<br />\n使領館表示，通常在一年內舉辦兩場財物拍賣和車輛拍賣，但由於疫情的關係，延至昨日才舉辦今年首場拍賣。<br />\n<br />\n原文網址：<a href=\"https://www.881903.com/news/china/2350726\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.881903.com%2Fnews%2Fchina%2F2350726&d=Iz1eZ%2FSDqTYQUikxH7ZeakUPjIZJXyGGplxIPwZjN5A%3D&h=7bff1194\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.881903.com/news/china/2350726</a>"},{"pid":"d4e9d73f808699e0e05edb54ef4c5fa76736b53d","tid":2140713,"uid":39365,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-05T07:35:24.000Z","msg":"講左撤離就撤離唔到架啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"95241947c6d7f281b64a4e71cf2ae442f5882290","tid":2140713,"uid":18477,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-05T07:35:29.000Z","msg":"真真假假<br />\n假假真真"},{"pid":"5e955bf1ab5641f4496624d340eef1448c518d70","tid":2140713,"uid":173945,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-05T07:36:10.000Z","msg":"冇事<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wine.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5f9669bf785d396bf215672db85a778a2f9d9ffc","tid":2140713,"uid":260549,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-08-05T07:36:44.000Z","msg":"Never believe in anything until it is officially denied."},{"pid":"72f73f492d66327034ed645cfeb27565f6ce55c2","tid":2140713,"uid":50740,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-05T07:38:55.000Z","msg":"可能改做美軍基地呢"},{"pid":"a